In large skillet, cook", "onion", "in butter until tender.", "Remove onion to bowl with", "slotted spoon.", "In drippings, cook chicken until browned on both", "sides.", "Into", "chicken skillet measure 3 tablespoons parsley.", "Add", "onion,", "tomato", "sauce, water, wine, salt, pepper and basil.", "Bring quickly to a boil.", "Add shrimp; reduce heat to low; cover", "and", "simmer", "for 5 minutes or until chicken and shrimp are tender.", "Serve with rice.", "Serves 6."]
